Ravi,

The question about Lucene's case-sensitivity is a moot one- it=
 depends on 
the analyzers/filters you use. If you use StandardAnalyzer (which=
 you don't 
have to), a lowercase filter is applied, hence the lack of 
case-sensitivity.

Regards,
Kelvin


