Subject: RE: Are score values always between 0 and 1?
Date: Tue, 15 Oct 2002 08:31:54 -0400
Organization: LISSUS llc
Message-ID: <004801c27446$d9b696f0$0801000a@Lissus>
MIME-Version: 1.0
