Terry,

What you typically want to do is something along the lines of 

BitSet bits =3D new BitSet(reader.maxDoc());
Term t =3D new Term(field, fieldValue);
TermDocs termDocs =3D reader.termDocs(t);
try
{
    while (termDocs.next())
    {
        int docNumber =3D termDocs.doc();
        bits.set(docNumber);
    }
}
finally
{
    if (termDocs !=3D null) termDocs.close();
}

this searches for all documents containing the term t, then=
 allowing these 
documents to be returned (note: everything else is disallowed by=
 default).

Regards,
Kelvin


